🎯 Features
✅ JWT-based Admin Authentication
✅ Medicine Management (CRUD operations)
✅ Billing System with Cart
✅ Inventory Alerts
✅ Sales History & Invoice Generation
✅ Dashboard with Analytics
✅ OOP Implementation with Classes
✅ Responsive Modern UI
