🚀 Installation & Setup
Prerequisites
Node.js (v14+)
npm or yarn
Backend Setup
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev
Backend runs on http://localhost:5000

Seed Database: Database is automatically seeded with sample data on first run.

Frontend Setup
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
Frontend runs on http://localhost:5173

